data.clean_description: This listing is for fourteen grams of trimmings and some smaller untrimmed buds. I only save the trim with lots of visible trichomes and throw the rest away. This trim would be great for making wax , shatter , butane hash oil , Rick Simpson oil , edibles or filling blunts. Trim has a leafy taste compared to the bud and is less potent. Shipping is by Priority Mail. I only ship to US states and territories. Your order will arrive double vacuum sealed and inside a sealed mylar / mbb bag. I try to ensure that the buds are not crushed during shipping and I always weigh it a little over.
data.name: 2oz Assorted Trim
